        "story_heading": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Born from a love of Korean beauty rituals</h2>",
            "width": "100%",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "h3"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "story_body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Seoul Glow Lab was founded by skincare obsessives who grew up layering essences, double-cleansing, and chasing that elusive glass-skin finish. We\u2019ve spent years studying what makes K-beauty work\u2014and distilling it into a simple, effective routine anyone can follow.</p><p>Every product we make starts with one question: <em>would we use this ourselves?</em> If it doesn\u2019t feel luxurious, perform visibly, and pass our ingredient standards, it doesn\u2019t make the cut.</p>",
            "width": "narrow",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "rte"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
